      "span_text": "The program identifies regions in protein sequences with a K a /K s ratio significantly greater than 1 as positively selected and those with the K a /K s ratio significantly smaller than 1 are considered as areas of purifying selection, and the randomly mutated regions have K a /K s ratio close to 1"
